Body: Sure, for the purpose of transfer of an investor’s exchange account to a trader in trust management, an API key provided by the exchange is used. The API key is not transferred to the trader, but stored on Membrana’s platform in a secure database. To conclude the transaction between investors and traders an Ethereum Smart Contract is used. All contracts concluded by traders via the Membrana platform will be saved to the database. It`s a short version of determination what the trust is. You could also check the whitepaper for more info.

Body: Sure, one example is the technology implemented on the Membrana platform provides fund security for investors - funds are transferred to traders in trust management. The funds are not directly transferred to traders under any circumstances, nor do traders have access to investors’ API keys. API keys are stored on the Membrana platform in a secure database. Traders carry out transactions via the single trading terminal on Membrana platform. Each trust management contract has specific currency restrictions which are available for trading, thus, it is impossible for traders to utilize investors’ funds for a dummy currency.

Hi there, it is perfect news for you  1)  7th May release Beta v.0.1, include: - New core architechture; - Dividing 1 API key for several traders; - Traders payout in ETH. Risk management system with: - Stop loss mechanics; - Target profit; - Crash close (prohibited investor action).  2) 15th May we start KYC for Global Traders Competition  3) 15th June we start Global Traders Competition  4) 30th June awarding first TOP5 traders and announce this at our social networks  ======== Membrana is announcing Global Traders Competition! Every week from the start of the competition, traders will receive money for trading on Membrana platform to compete with each other. This is real trading with real money! At the end of each competitive week, 5 best traders will receive: 1. All of their winnings on Ethereum wallet; 2. Tournament points, depending on their rank position; 3. Official Membana hoodie; 4. Entry ticket for Membrana meetup event.  Tournament point will be equal to Membrana platform tokens, so that participants will receive bonuses not only in Ethereum, but also in platform tokens. For the record, Membrana tokens wont be sold through any crowdsale, so their availability is strongly limited.  We invite all traders to participate in this competition! Follow the updates!  Quote Maybe Membrana will really change the world for the better ... Such a revolutionary approach can not be left without attention and results Time is show   BTC

Author: Membrana.io
Title: 🚀 [ANN] HOT IEO !!! MEMBRANA - TRUST AND ASSET MANAGEMENT OF DIGITAL ASSETS
Body: The trader doesn’t need to pay for anything. When concluding a contract between an investor and a trader, the investor transfers the maximum commission of the trader to the smart contract of the platform in advance. The remuneration is not transferred to the trader, but is stored in the smart contract until the completion of the contract. After the end of the contract and the financial result achieved by the trader, the remuneration is transferred to him. If the trader reaches only half of the target profit, he gets half of his reward, the rest is returned to the investor.

Author: Membrana.io
Title: 🚀 [ANN] HOT IEO !!! MEMBRANA - TRUST AND ASSET MANAGEMENT OF DIGITAL ASSETS
Body: >>> HOT IEO on ABCC exchange! <<<  Important Links: Website | Beta version | Forum | Github | Whitepaper | Twitter | Telegram   Membrana.io Trust management of digital assets  Membrana is a transparent, blockchain-based ecosystem to work with financial markets and to conclude contracts for trust management. We empower everyone with a secure opportunity to receive financial freedom!  On current stage of development we introduce you Beta version of Membrana platform, available on the link below:  Beta - https://beta.membrana.io     Objective  The main objective of Membrana platform is to directly connect an investor and a trader to conclude a mutually beneficial, secure, and reliable contract.  To avoid risks for an investor and a trader, such as fraud, lack of trust and other counterparty risks and to make cooperation under trust management more profitable and safe, here at Membrana we have developed a unique algorithm which provide users such opportunities:  Membrana platform allows an investor to give traders an opportunity to manage funds, but not possessing the funds. Also, investors do not transfer their funds to Membrana platform Traders get access for trading through unique interface, which works with exchanges through API protocol. Investor set all the restrictions for this key, including which cryptocurrencies are available for trading.  All parameters of the deal, such as target profit, duration of the contract, maximum trading loss, etc are deployed in Ethereum smart contract, which controls granting an access for trading and holds trader’s commission fee to the time contract is finished. Rating system is integrated in Membrana platform, where all traders and investors are ranked by their finished contracts and ROI (return of investment). Investors can easily choose suitable trader, based on complete and definitive information about his achievements. Users can be sure of getting reliable data on past activities, because it is confirmed by a hash sum of transactions saved in blockchain.  You can read more about the principles of platform operation in Membrana WhitePaper.   Roadmap of Membrana project  Q1 2017 CONCEPT GENERATION Q2 2017 PERFORMANCE AUDIT Q3 2017 INTERFACE CREATION Q1 2018 ALPHA VERSION Q2 2018 BETA VERSION Q3 2018 MAJOR UPDATE Q4 2018 PUBLIC PRE-SALE Q1 2019 CONDITIONAL ORDERS AND UI UPDATE Q2 2019 IEO Q3 2019 ADVANCED FEATURES Q4 2019 FINAL RELEASE Q2 2020 ADDITIONAL FEATURES Q1 2021 STOCK MARKET EXPANSION   You can read detailed roadmap here: https://membrana.io/roadmap   Development waypoints achieved  Concept Generation: done Performance Audit: done Interface Creation: done Demo Version: done Alpha Version: done Beta Version: done Major Beta update: done Conditional orders release: done UI/UX update: done   Why invest in Membrana  Product. Working product (Public Beta) with over 3000 customers. Desktop and Mobile versions are released. Already 2888 trust management contracts concluded with $1,6M trading volume. Final release in Q4 2019. Rewards. Stake MBN tokens to receive profit in MBN tokens and BTC Team. Expert development team from Russia and worldwide network of brand managers and ambassadors. Supported by top experts from JP Morgan, CME, Goldman Sachs. Listing confirmed. Listing on 3 exchanges on 17th June - ABCC, KRX exchange, Probit Community. High ratings on ICO trackers and big community - 80k telegram users. 2 US venture funds have already invested into the company. (Coinbar group and Firstblock Ventures)  Token usage  The Membrana token (MBN) is an ERC-20 compliant token to be issued on the Ethereum blockchain. The MBN token model is giving different kind of utilities, which offers interacting with the platform and directly with other users.  Additionally, there are multiple staking features, which allows users to receive rewards, benefits and governance of community operated fund. Customers are encouraged to stake tokens or use tokens as a payment method providing organic growth of token ecosystem.
